    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i should see a doctor but i'm just so busy with work and my clinic is a trek. it's probably just the humidity in mumbai making it harder to breathe, right? maybe i can just take an extra puff of my salbutamol twice a day for a week and see if that fixes it?",
