      "content": "a brisk walk?? i can barely walk to the kitchen without feeling like my chest is tight lol. i'm not sure if i'm even up for a walk right now. honestly i'm just feeling really tired and a bit dizzy too. is it possible my asthma is just flaring up because of the pollution and i'll be fine if i just rest and maybe take some extra antihistamines to clear my airways? it's probably nothing serious, right?",
